{"tid":2209801,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美議員提案授權動武護台","createTime":"2020-09-20T01:59:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T02:08:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"22b6334f8ea65d7ea909e0d9fe6760419d3ba8e7","tid":2209801,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T01:59:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200920/JWDRFZAWOVBPZNSBBBC2ESSQTU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200920%2FJWDRFZAWOVBPZNSBBBC2ESSQTU%2F&d=1nW%2FAbATR%2BcU2iH%2BEMdxEwWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=799d4f49\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200920%2FJWDRFZAWOVBPZNSBBBC2ESSQTU%2F&h=8b741ee8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200920/JWDRFZAWOVBPZNSBBBC2ESSQTU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美議員提案授權動武護台<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eB_2li99WRHCfH_pvPbzfnejDq0=/720x642/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RZODLNA4NZE6PCNYANNCROYXMU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeB_2li99WRHCfH_pvPbzfnejDq0%3D%2F720x642%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRZODLNA4NZE6PCNYANNCROYXMU.jpg&h=fb389489&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國總統特朗普<br />\n<br />\n北京頻頻軍事脅逼台灣，美國兩黨有議員撐台，共和黨參議員史考特（Rick Scott）前天（18日）提出「防止台灣遭侵略法案」（Taiwan Invasion Prevention Act），授權美國總統在中國武力犯台時得動用武力防衞台灣，法案也鼓勵美國總統與國務卿訪台。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鼓勵美總統國務卿訪台<br />\n<br />\n法案給予美國總統有限國防授權，在台灣遭受中國大陸直接武力襲擊、借武力奪取台灣實質管轄領土，以及台灣人民、軍人遇害，。。。。。。。。。。。。總統在美國國會發表演說。法案也敦促美國貿易代表在法案生效後180天內，與台灣就雙邊貿易協定展開協商。<br />\n<br />\n這個法案與聯邦眾議院外委會亞太小組共和黨首席議員約霍（Ted Yoho）於7月底提出的同名法案內容。。。。。。。。。。。。。。國際盟友的承諾，重申美國在印太地區的安全承諾，確保所有國家在國際水域和空域行使權利」等。<br />\n<br />\n美國之音<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NudoqticBZvFNLSjAXjSZo2nlJk=/1446x844/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BBKRYD4KNJETNJ6G76GY272MVM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNudoqticBZvFNLSjAXjSZo2nlJk%3D%2F1446x844%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBBKRYD4KNJETNJ6G76GY272MVM.gif&h=985f8a1c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39e55cfabb60bbf60b1b195f4b59f982aaa0ca34","tid":2209801,"uid":175673,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T02:01:50.000Z","msg":"Go ahead. it is bored"},{"pid":"b3ca097c5eb2b62197b0c78b734a07558b74edff","tid":2209801,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T02:02:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c29b7a834374d61d2bf63e4f7b7b81e5a2df2dee","tid":2209801,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T02:02:27.000Z","msg":"要來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63f5c0f338ca577a1081c1ed127def8e55620e7","tid":2209801,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T02:03:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88d17e750d65eade8201f93a7d3c981f6582593a","tid":2209801,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T02:06:45.000Z","msg":"美軍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ec34df15c107343ef1b84974364b3fd5dbb0ef","tid":2209801,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T02:07:45.000Z","msg":"去印度前線都喊成咁<br />\n點打美軍呀？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft1aZ1ZT.png&amp;h=99c8ce27&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"9c7f9b18eea12bac20b3c5b6bac07fd805ddb55c","tid":2209801,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T02:08:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}